          "en": "OpenAI has introduced a Safety Bug Bounty program and announced plans for its Foundation to invest at least $1 billion in initiatives covering disease, economic opportunity, AI resilience, and community programs.",
          "zh": "OpenAI 推出安全漏洞奖励计划，并宣布其基金会计划至少投资 10 亿美元，用于疾病治疗、经济机会、AI 韧性及社区项目。"
        },
        "key_takeaways": {
          "en": [
            "OpenAI's Safety Bug Bounty program targets AI abuse and safety risks, including agentic vulnerabilities, prompt injection, and data exfiltration.",
            "The OpenAI Foundation plans to invest at least $1 billion.",
            "This investment will support initiatives in curing diseases, economic opportunity, AI resilience, and community programs."
          ],
          "zh": [
            "OpenAI 的安全漏洞奖励计划旨在识别 AI 滥用和安全风险，包括主体性漏洞、提示注入和数据窃取。",
            "OpenAI 基金会计划至少投资 10 亿美元。",
            "这笔投资将用于疾病治疗、经济机会、AI 韧性及社区项目。"
          ]
        },
        "impact": {
          "en": "These actions demonstrate OpenAI's dual focus on addressing the technical safety and ethical implications of AI development while also committing significant capital to broader societal benefits through its foundation. This dual approach aims to foster responsible AI advancement and application.",
          "zh": "这些行动表明 OpenAI 双重关注：既解决 AI 开发的技术安全和伦理问题，又通过其基金会承诺大量资金用于更广泛的社会效益。这种双重策略旨在促进负责任的 AI 进步和应用。"
        },
        "source": "OpenAI News",
        "link": "https://openai.com/index/safety-bug-bounty"
